{"tid":1184823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"米老鼠學位如廢紙 港女告英大學獲賠60萬","createTime":"2019-06-04T01:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T06:45:15.000Z","uid":256501,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a5a296daad8f39226c0ebd5c5ce951d022162db1","tid":1184823,"uid":256501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T01:28:13.000Z","msg":"維權無罪興訟有理，港女控告英大學學位如廢紙搵工碰壁，校方終賠款逾60萬港元。破天荒勝仗顯示學生對貨不對辦院校擁有追索權，同類訴訟可能陸續有來。<br />\n<br />\n現已回港的黃博(Pok Wong，音，30歲)就讀安格里亞魯斯金大學(Anglia Ruskin University)，屬中游級數，<span style=\"color: red;\">本港立法會議員何君堯亦為校友</span>。她於2011年修讀國際商務策略，兩年後以一級榮譽畢業，找工作卻屢受挫敗，斥沙紙如同廢紙，取得的只是「米奇老鼠學位」；又指該校章程宣稱「優質教育保障就業前途光明」，分明存在欺騙性誤導，去年入稟倫敦縣法院，要求賠償逾6萬英鎊學費、留學開支及堂費。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">雙方日前達成庭外和解，校方如數賠償，但指黃的訴訟並無理據，章程所指就業前景不等同「合約」，校方只是聽取保險公司意見了結官司。</span>黃曾指ARU教學質素差，講師經常遲到或要求學生自修，甚少講解學術而一味做選擇題。她期望藉此開創先例，讓學生支付高昂學費的同時，也獲得應有的價值。<br />\n<br />\n米奇老鼠學位一詞出自英前教育部長Margaret Hodge，意指那些不具學術價值、對學生職業全無幫助的學位，如高球管理、馬術心理學或冷門藝術等，然而在不少人眼中，這些課程卻如米老鼠般惹人喜愛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/share/174840\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fshare%2F174840&d=TytWRGNO3s0Eety5H3eok4lFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=7523a474\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/share/174840</a>"},{"pid":"2e607cc0e3c5f786b7f49b6cf66750af5911a5fa","tid":1184823,"uid":3311,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T01:30:07.000Z","msg":"馬術心理學<br />\n<br />\n原來真係有得讀動物傳心師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66f0200c9c59d51d585827d835cc97e622e878a","tid":1184823,"uid":7903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e607cc0e3c5f786b7f49b6cf66750af5911a5fa","tid":1184823,"uid":3311,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T01:30:07.000Z","msg":"馬術心理學<br />\n<br />\n原來真係有得讀動物傳心師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T01:31:44.000Z","msg":"呢啲馬會都唔會請<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa57bb777e2635a903fe8fce8a64d3f95d4f149","tid":1184823,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T01:55:03.000Z","msg":"香港都太把垃圾學店啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec7843a135b80d24137eb41fbfda6035e1893b5","tid":1184823,"uid":256501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T03:17:15.000Z","msg":"出奇在堂堂一間大學竟然讓步"},{"pid":"394903978deba45523bd5d59c24f424461e55319","tid":1184823,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ec7843a135b80d24137eb41fbfda6035e1893b5","tid":1184823,"uid":256501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T03:17:15.000Z","msg":"出奇在堂堂一間大學竟然讓步"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:01:16.000Z","msg":"揸返60萬仲開心啦"},{"pid":"a517972ad3a2263ad0926d4206244f19356b5acf","tid":1184823,"uid":26154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ec7843a135b80d24137eb41fbfda6035e1893b5","tid":1184823,"uid":256501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T03:17:15.000Z","msg":"出奇在堂堂一間大學竟然讓步"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:49:27.000Z","msg":"話唔定間野都身有屎驚上庭會迫佢地要disclose 呱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b8793cce48be18c3d33de13795348cc12f3d86","tid":1184823,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a517972ad3a2263ad0926d4206244f19356b5acf","tid":1184823,"uid":26154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ec7843a135b80d24137eb41fbfda6035e1893b5","tid":1184823,"uid":256501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T03:17:15.000Z","msg":"出奇在堂堂一間大學竟然讓步"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:49:27.000Z","msg":"話唔定間野都身有屎驚上庭會迫佢地要disclose 呱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:55:23.000Z","msg":"佢上堂敗訴 之後賠撚死<br />\n個個都告鳩佢<br />\n佢而家和解左 無咁多手尾"},{"pid":"68d1aa8a26ea9c0c616bf5